OL,6,F"It just goes on and on and on.
OL,8,F"That was supposed to be their best
OL,9,Foffer and now it means prolonging the
OL,10,Fprocess even further, for myself and
OL,11,Fhundreds of others.
OL,13,F"I am one of hundreds of sub-
OL,14,Fpostmasters who have refused their
OL,15,Fcompensation offers. I will need to
OL,16,Ftalk to my solicitors about next
OL,17,Fsteps."
