OL,3,CPost Office campaigner Alan Bates to
OL,4,Creject 'offensive' compensation offer
OL,6,FHe said the offer had been made on
OL,7,FWednesday, 111 days after his claim `
OL,8,Fprepared with the help of forensic
OL,9,Faccountants engaged by his lawyers `
OL,10,Fhad been submitted.
OL,12,F"I have been in the queue along with
OL,13,Fall the others in the scheme, but if
OL,14,Fmy case is an example of the way they
OL,15,Fare going to treat all cases, we may
OL,16,Fas well start looking at a legal
OL,17,Faction again and let the judiciary
OL,18,Fdecide," he said.
