OL,6,FMr Bates was among more than 500
OL,7,Fpeople who received an average of
OL,8,Fabout #20,000 after a High Court
OL,9,Fruling in 2019.
OL,11,FA government spokesman told the
OL,12,FTelegraph: "If any applicant to the
OL,13,FGLO (Group Litigation Order) scheme
OL,14,Ffeels that they are owed more than is
OL,15,Fbeing offered, we are happy to discuss
OL,16,Fthe evidence with their legal advisers.
